ConstValues.value:
"OpenWebIAUSDK: NimbusSDK setup is invalid!
Please ensure NimbusSDK 'BUILD_LIBRARY_FOR_DISTRIBUTION' is set to 'YES'
If you're using Cocoa Pods then you might want to add it in the post-install script:

post_install do |installer|
  installer.pods_project.targets.each do |target|
    target.build_configurations.each do |config|
      if target.name == 'NimbusSDK'
        config.build_settings['BUILD_LIBRARY_FOR_DISTRIBUTION'] = 'YES'
      end
    end
  end
end
"
